data.description: Great opportunity to own this charming, easy to maintain home that features a private rear yard that  backs to trees and a common area. 2 spacious bedrooms and full bath as well as updated tiled kitchen and bath. Also has newer LVP flooring, windows and siding - experience a living space that is not only visually appealing but also easy to maintain. Stay organized with plentiful storage options, including  attic, basement, and a convenient shed. Situated in the heart of a vibrant community, this home is just a stone's throw away from the park, Elizabethtown College, and the bustling downtown of Etown. Enjoy the best of both worlds – a peaceful neighborhood and easy access to local amenities. Don't miss the chance to make this home your own – a prime location, and a peaceful ambiance. Schedule your showing today!
